## Button Component

All clickable actions must use `<Button>` from `@/components/ui/Button`.

### Variants

| Variant         | When to use                                  |
| --------------- | -------------------------------------------- |
| `primary`       | Primary CTA (default). Gradient fill.        |
| `outline`       | Secondary action, ghost with border.         |
| `surface`       | CTA on dark/gradient backgrounds (white bg). |
| `ghost-inverse` | On primary-gradient backgrounds, no fill.    |

### Sizes

| Size | Padding / text    | When to use                   |
| ---- | ----------------- | ----------------------------- |
| `sm` | px-6 py-2.5 / sm  | Navbar, compact areas         |
| `md` | px-6 py-3.5 / sm  | Forms, card actions (default) |
| `lg` | px-10 py-4 / base | Section CTAs                  |
| `xl` | px-10 py-5 / lg   | Hero actions                  |

### Props

- `pill` ‚Äì adds `rounded-full` (use for navbar-style pills)
- `className` ‚Äì for one-off overrides (e.g. `w-full`, `rounded-xl`)

```tsx
// ‚úÖ Correct
<Button variant="primary" size="xl">Upload File</Button>
<Button variant="outline" size="sm" pill>Get Started</Button>
<Button variant="surface" size="lg" className="w-full">Start Free Trial</Button>

// ‚ùå Wrong ‚Äî raw <button> with inline Tailwind
<button className="bg-linear-to-br from-primary ... px-10 py-5 rounded-2xl font-headline font-bold">
  Upload File
</button>
```

