## Typography Conventions

- **Headings:** `font-headline` (Manrope) + `font-bold` or `font-semibold`
- **Body:** `font-body` (Inter) + `font-light` or default weight
- **Labels / badges:** `font-headline font-semibold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest`
- **Line-height for large headings:** add `leading-[1.1]` or `leading-tight`

---

## Spacing & Layout

- Section bottom margin: `mb-32` or `mb-40`
- Card padding: `p-8` (default) or `p-10` (generous)
- Card border radius: `rounded-[2rem]` for cards, `rounded-3xl` for modals
- Max widths: `max-w-7xl` (page), `max-w-5xl` (narrow sections), `max-w-2xl` (copy)
